<item>
            <title>[SOLR-16357] CaffeineCache ramBytes incorrect accounting on updates and deletes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16357</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;CaffeineCache ramBytes accounting is incorrect on deletes and updates over exiting values.&lt;br/&gt;
2 problematic scenarios:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;updates over existing value will double-add the key&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;deletes will double-delete: once due to manual bookkeeping in the remove method and second due to the onRemoval callback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
